data.description:
Better than new with no wait from the builder! This Popular Senita plan features flowing, open space & 3 true split bedrooms. This home is
highlighted by a comfortable owner's suite with roomy walk-in closet and a modern tiled walk-in shower. The kitchen features granite counters and white
cabinets. A meticulous backyard awaits, with the perfect blend of style & practicality W/ low-maintenance turf that requires minimal upkeep, you can enjoy the
beauty of lush greenery w/o the hassle. Stay cool in the summer with a full-length patio cover. No rear neighbors gives you ultimate privacy. Other upgrades
include plantation Shutters, lighting package & ceiling fan pre-plumbs, Paver driveway extension, Garage service door, water softener, & cathedral insulation
ceiling barrier in the attic. Other upgrades include plantation Shutters, lighting package & ceiling fan pre-plumbs, Paver driveway extension, Garage service door, water softener, & cathedral insulation ceiling barrier in the attic.
Live, work, and play in the GROWING master planned community of Anthem Merrill Ranch Parkside. All ages are welcome to enjoy the many amenities including, 43,000 SF Community Center featuring fitness center, full court gym, rock wall, 2 outdoor pools, and Water Park. Or enjoy our park featuring amphitheater, children's playground and splash pad. Softball fields and soccer fields play host to many unique and fun events all year round, come see this amazing community for yourself!
